<bibRefCitation author="Disney RHL" box="[889,1026,1316,1340]" pageId="4" pageNumber="1603" pagination="1 - 155" refId="ref8043" refString="Disney RHL. 1989. Scuttle Flies - Diptera Phoridae Genus Megaselia. Handbk Ident Br Insects. 10: 1 - 155." type="journal article" year="1989">Disney 1989</bibRefCitation>
) (see below).
